## ğŸš€ Quick Start (5 Minutes)

### Step 1: Install Dependencies
```bash
cd backend
npm install
```

### Step 2: Start Redis (Secure)
```bash
# In terminal 1
cd backend
redis-server redis/redis.conf
```

You should see:
```
âœ… Server initialized
âœ… Ready to accept connections (TLS)
```

### Step 3: Start Backend API
```bash
# In terminal 2
cd backend
npm start
```

You should see:
```
ğŸš€ ZeroPay Secure Backend API
   Status: PRODUCTION SECURE âœ…
   âœ… TLS 1.3 for Redis
   âœ… AES-256-GCM encryption at rest
```

